      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "All interface type — headlines (40/56px, weight 500), subheads (24px, weight 500), body and UI (14/16px, weight 400), nav links (12/14px). The geometric grotesque with tight -0.02em tracking gives industrial precision; weight 500 (not 700) for display type keeps the system restrained rather than shouty."
